{"tid":32302,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"條女成日上黎我屋企煮飯 搞到我洗多左好多錢!!!","createTime":"2016-12-10T06:12:40.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T06:36:46.000Z","uid":30922,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7dd8d69628195d576e6b81f9560d9bb2b2810537","tid":32302,"uid":30922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:12:40.000Z","msg":"條友成日話肚餓 但又唔想出去食 我問想點 佢話上黎我屋企煮 <br />\n<br />\n上黎就2手空空 打開我雪櫃就自己拎D野出黎煮 今朝就煮撚左我塊STEAK <br />\n<br />\n成$2X 佢仲煮D菜 用下SAUCE 加埋水電煤 一餐都煮我好撚多 <br />\n<br />\n我真係計撚住佢 佢有時又煮下公仔面 煎下野 雖然係次次都煮埋我果份 <br />\n<br />\n但我忍唔住 岩岩問佢拎番錢 佢話:你講真架? <br />\n<br />\n我: 係 你加加埋埋都煮我好撚多錢 真係要比番我 <br />\n<br />\n佢: 你痴線架? 咁樣問女朋友拎番錢 <br />\n<br />\n我: 你走先 我想一個人冷靜下 <br />\n<br />\n之後到而家10粒鐘我地都冇講過野 我真係唔知點面對佢 有冇人可以教我點做?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"341a9cc93f2c699d5a870926a96e270b93a307ff","tid":32302,"uid":20908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:13:49.000Z","msg":"咪咁撚小家喇"},{"pid":"3145b30d63a086af3b92f56b7c1002adf5c3ff48","tid":32302,"uid":1554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:14:18.000Z","msg":"回帶"},{"pid":"bc2af234e37595fbac43619d0c927574638702b9","tid":32302,"uid":53966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:15:33.000Z","msg":"點解你可以計住計住你女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b8fbb9f825729dc3b9a7d1957086d3a9a8e47d5","tid":32302,"uid":7482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:17:19.000Z","msg":"好多真心膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"928bee272946b9d6a3579e77031b062844939e45","tid":32302,"uid":54216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:17:53.000Z","msg":"煮埋比你都咁柒多野講"},{"pid":"25541c9611903f757cacc5bec17fad854cc592ea","tid":32302,"uid":61077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:18:21.000Z","msg":"我記得有煮龍蝦架喎？"},{"pid":"2b